      "summary": "Auth state management is exposed as mutable package-global state (`ClientManager`), forcing other modules to depend on global variables instead of stable interfaces.",
      "related_files": ["goseg/auth/auth.go", "goseg/broadcast/broadcast.go", "goseg/importer/importer.go"],
